general.headline: Crypto funds smash records with $5.95B inflows amid shutdown concerns

general.headline: Nvidia's Sky-High AI Ambitions Under Fire: Goldman Sachs Flags 'Circular Revenue' Risk As Wall Street Questions 'Jensen's Math' - NVIDIA  ( NASDAQ:NVDA )
